2005-04-12 [colin]	1.9.6cvs34

	* src/prefs_account.c
		Fix smtp auth type off-by-one. We forgot to
		add PLAIN in the prefs-to-gui setter func and
		as a result, the selected auth when opening
		account prefs was not the correct one.

